Package clientSide.entities

Class PendingAdjustment

  • java.lang.Object
    • clientSide.entities.PendingAdjustment
  • public class PendingAdjustment
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a pending adjustment for a park. This class stores information about a specific adjustment including the ID of the adjustment, park details (ID, name, and department), the date and time of the adjustment, who adjusted it, the parameter value before and after the adjustment, and the type of parameter adjusted.

        Parameters:
        adjusmentId - The unique ID of the adjustment.
        parkId - The ID of the park where the adjustment is made.
        parkName - The name of the park.
        department - The department within the park that is responsible for the adjustment.
        dayOfAdjusting - The date when the adjustment was made.
        timeOfAdjusting - The time when the adjustment was made.
        adjustedBy - The identifier of the individual who made the adjustment.
        parameterBefore - The value of the parameter before the adjustment.
        parameterAfter - The value of the parameter after the adjustment.
        parameterType - The type of the parameter that was adjusted.
